===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛlə|-ɛlə]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Cloth-covered frame used for [[protection]] against [[rain]] or [[sun]].
# Generally, anything that provides protection. (''The fighters provide a defensive air umbrella over the battle group.'')
# Something that covers a wide range of concepts, ideas, purposes, etc. (''The test facility was established under the umbrella of the company's quality program.'')
# The main body of a [[jellyfish]], excluding the [[tentacle]]s.

